            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-2339.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to J. D. Hooker, 12 [October 1858]</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f5">See also <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 6, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-2136.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to Asa Gray, 5 September [1857]</ref>, in which CD told Gray about <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1585.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Hugh Falconer’s</ref> remark.</note>
